        <abstract> 
<p>Wishes CD could publish <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> with footnotes.</p>  
<p>Increases in bird populations: starlings are increasing, but AN cannot give reason; mistletoe-thrush increasing but not ousting song-thrush. Doubts trustworthiness of [George?] Edwards, CD’s authority in <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> on this matter [see <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, 6th ed., p. 59].</p> 
            <p>AN opposed to bird protection legislation to prohibit egging. Argues egging does not decrease number of birds.</p>
        </abstract>
